719973f-a.folder: Gansevoort Street & Washington Street, Manhattan, NY

724218f-a.text:
1. Washington Street and Gansevoort Market Stand, north from No. 811 Washington Street, adjoining the S.E. corner of Gansevoort Street, and showing a view to Little West 12th Street. November 12, 1933. P. L. Sperr.

2. The same, at a later date, and showing the elevated railroad tracks completed. April 10, 1934. P. L. Sperr.

3. The same. Washington Street North of Gansevoort,from a point farther South,showing the Gansevoort Market Place. May 12th, I940.
P. L. Sperr.
